{"tid":1618002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]反緊急法，唔好講反禁蒙面法","createTime":"2019-10-04T03:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T04:41:18.000Z","uid":97181,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c706bee44f78a1fc37f35ee1c6d0ff3f0e74ad55","tid":1618002,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:32:45.000Z","msg":"我地反對的唔係禁蒙面法呢條法例<br />\n係政府用緊急法黎繞過立法會<br />\n大家記住三權分立先係法治基石<br />\n如果政府用緊急法取代立法會功能<br />\n他日亦可以取代法院功能<br />\n即係球證旁證球員對手連隊友觀眾啤酒妹掃地阿伯都係對面的人<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">極權緊急法<br />\n殺人都合法</span></strong>"},{"pid":"67352642d5baafe924834e731d13644f6504595c","tid":1618002,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:33:41.000Z","msg":"push 1/20"},{"pid":"4151cdcf4de1e917f18aac392053d4ecf919c19f","tid":1618002,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"推呢個，而家要推出去其他social media，要快<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蒙面引緊急 = 送台立送中</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617984</a>"},{"pid":"a0d15ed13f50d43fca19f623e4b9b63c50e189c2","tid":1618002,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n所有人都要知"},{"pid":"3abf4311e2386d13c253df7b1e35c65cbcdecb26","tid":1618002,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0d15ed13f50d43fca19f623e4b9b63c50e189c2","tid":1618002,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n所有人都要知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"點解都未立就吹晒風好似已經接受咗咁？係想大家唔好反抗匆匆立咗先，唔好俾佢立呀！<br />\n<br />\n推呢個，而家要推出去其他social media，要快<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蒙面引緊急 = 送台立送中</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"http